
  Swinub    Ice Type Pokémon

  It rubs its snout on the ground 
  to find and dig up food.  It 
  sometimes discovers hot springs. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Swinub ► Piloswine ► Mamoswine

   ↞--------| STATS |--------↠ 
